{"tid":2443800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國據報禁向華為出口5G產品 中方反對","createTime":"2021-03-12T09:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T08:36:27.000Z","uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ce14cc2355d30e9e79de1e0d1e8050dc9a21dcff","tid":2443800,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:24:33.000Z","msg":"美國據報禁向華為出口5G產品 中方批美不擇手段打壓<br />\n<br />\n彭博社消息指，美國政府已通知一些華為供應商，禁止向華為出口5G設備相關產品。在北京，外交部批評，美方濫用國家力量，不擇手段打壓中國高科技企業，嚴重違反市場經濟和公平競爭原則。發言人趙立堅說，事實一再表明，美國是一個不可靠、沒有信用的國家，做法不僅損害中國企業的合法權益，也損害美國和其他國家企業的利益，中方促請美方立即停止對中國企業的無理打壓，公平公正、非歧視地對待中國企業，多做有利於中美科技交流和經貿合作的事。<br />\n<br />\n2021-03-12 17:14:44"},{"pid":"6b256dcaf1b7f9229d6d1daedc1b380b8ddc2762","tid":2443800,"uid":44171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:26:07.000Z","msg":"美國內政，中國人為什麼喜歡說三道四？"},{"pid":"e3dc75ff15049661d4a444702bf782f6ee755875","tid":2443800,"uid":119756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"大和田"},{"pid":"f8b0ec794a69e5136daab2bf68e066fc2e4dc118","tid":2443800,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:27:12.000Z","msg":"迷侵力：All Talk. No Action. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b79cc165191f9c6c5f84663986b5c4ed6f2f6a2","tid":2443800,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:29:18.000Z","msg":"美國<span class=\"xx-large\">據報</span>禁向華為出口5G產品 中方批美不擇手段打壓<br />\n<br />\n做咗先講唔該"},{"pid":"21b195348932aa702aeb23bea48b114b9ffcc05e","tid":2443800,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:29:42.000Z","msg":"ATNA"},{"pid":"97b7c8b25dd427a074c7e4db57208a6070d79a51","tid":2443800,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T09:30:36.000Z","msg":"敗登: 知道, 對唔住大